    "description": "A satrapy of the Achaemenid Persian empire established in Thrace in 513 BC by Darius I and Megabazus and abandoned in 479 BC following the failure of Xerxes' invasion of Greece. It was a minor satrapy, subordinate to the central main satrapy of Lydia. ",
